IMPORTANT NOTICE FOR MEDICAL USE:

This software is intended for medical workflow automation and should be used
in accordance with applicable medical device regulations and data protection
laws (GDPR, HIPAA, etc.). The authors assume no liability for medical decisions
made based on this software's output. Always verify generated reports and
measurements manually before clinical use.

This software handles sensitive patient data. Ensure compliance with:
- GDPR (Europe)
- HIPAA (US)
- Local data protection regulations
- Medical device certification requirements if applicable

Keep all patient data on secure, isolated local networks. Do not expose
DICOM servers to the public internet without proper security measures.
